hi! I'm trying to create a code to duplicate a part of the template. For this I was inspired a code that duplicates table rows.<br />
<br />
Basically use [0] at the beginning and end of the content that I want to duplicate, it actually copies the part you want, the problem is that the syntax error in the document, can someone tell me how to solve this?<br />
<pre><code>public function clonePart($search, $numberOfClones){
        $string = $this-&gt;_documentXML;
        $valor = '';
        for ($i = 1; $i &lt;= $numberOfClones; $i++) {
         $valor .= preg_replace(&quot;/.*\[\d+](.*)\[\d+].*/&quot;, &quot;$1&quot;, $string, 1);
        }
        $this-&gt;_documentXML =  htmlspecialchars($valor);
        echo $valor;
    }</code></pre>

